devdoc.details: Store game data and manage developer staking requirements

buyGameLicense(uint256).details: Buy a license for a game. This function would handle the transfer of funds and the assignment of the game license to the buyer.

params._gameId: The ID of the game for which to buy a license.

checkLicense(uint256,address).details: Check if an address owns a license for a particular game.

params._gameId: The ID of the game to check.

returns._0: bool indicating whether the address owns a license for the game.
